1
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:16,700
I've never thought
that the legendary prodigy,

2
00:00:16,710 --> 00:00:18,670
Young Master Zhuge
of Great Yong's Zhuge family,

3
00:00:18,670 --> 00:00:20,070
would fall to this point.

4
00:00:20,550 --> 00:00:20,870
Wasn't he

5
00:00:20,870 --> 00:00:22,670
the most feared spy master?

6
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:25,440
How could he end up so badly wounded?

7
00:00:29,670 --> 00:00:30,390
Xing,

8
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,850
I know you have many questions,

9
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:35,390
and I should give you some explanation.

10
00:00:35,390 --> 00:00:36,920
But I have my reasons not to.

11
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:39,140
Wait for me to settle everything.

12
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,390
Zhuge Yue,

13
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:48,200
can you stay for me?

14
00:00:51,430 --> 00:00:52,070
Yes.

15
00:00:52,430 --> 00:00:53,430
You're right.

16
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:56,470
But this is my business.

17
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:58,520
It has nothing to do with you.

18
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:16,400
I didn't even notice
your forbearance and pain.

19
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,950
And I've been resenting and blaming you

20
00:01:18,950 --> 00:01:19,750
all this time,

21
00:01:20,070 --> 00:01:21,510
never once thinking about

22
00:01:21,510 --> 00:01:23,590
how much hardship you've endured.

23
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:25,310
If he intended not to tell you,

24
00:01:25,310 --> 00:01:26,510
fearing you'd worry,

25
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,539
you naturally wouldn't know.

26
00:01:43,740 --> 00:01:45,430
This poison in him is very strange,

27
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:47,280
twisting along his heart meridians
and limbs,

28
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,479
yet it moves like thread.

29
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:50,789
I've tried my best but couldn't remove it.

30
00:01:50,789 --> 00:01:53,000
For now, I can only use needles
to seal his acupoints

31
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,789
to protect his organs,

32
00:01:55,789 --> 00:01:57,229
but how long this will hold

33
00:01:57,229 --> 00:01:58,710
depends on his own strength.

34
00:01:58,710 --> 00:01:59,430
Your Highness,

35
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:01,000
what should we do with our plan

36
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,070
to rescue General He?

37
00:02:02,070 --> 00:02:03,670
We don't have much time left.

38
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,120
At this point,

39
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:06,950
we can only wait for He Xiao

40
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:08,520
to be handed over to the Black Eagle Army

41
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:12,210
and look for an opportunity
when they're on the way back to Great Yan.

42
00:02:12,210 --> 00:02:15,940
Tomorrow, I'll go with Fang Miaomiao
to gather information first.

43
00:03:35,770 --> 00:03:40,950
[REBIRTH]

44
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:44,010
[Episode 15]

45
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:44,960
[Lincheng]

46
00:03:56,430 --> 00:03:58,030
Once the Yong Army opens the gate,

47
00:03:58,030 --> 00:04:01,030
and the Great Yan prisoners of war
walk out through it,

48
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:02,410
we'll be able to locate

49
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:03,870
He Xiao.

50
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,680
Open the gate!

51
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:41,790
They're coming.

52
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,510
He Xiao!

53
00:04:53,330 --> 00:04:54,840
Oh no, it's a trap!

54
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,170
Close the city gate!

55
00:04:56,850 --> 00:04:57,380
Hurry!

56
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,040
Charge!

57
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,740
What's that sound?

58
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,950
Something must have happened.

59
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:17,410
Don't get up. I'll go help.

60
00:05:58,990 --> 00:05:59,830
[He Xiao, General of Xiuli Army]

61
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,060
General Chu!

62
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:03,820
Get on the horse!

63
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:04,380
Yes!

64
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:06,630
Stop those three!

65
00:06:07,110 --> 00:06:08,520
Don't let them escape!

66
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:28,160
He Xiao, Miaomiao, you go first!

67
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,680
I'll cover you!

68
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,630
My Lord, you can't do that!

69
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:30,360
It's an order!

70
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:30,950
Your Highness!

71
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:31,510
Go!

72
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:41,510
Run!

73
00:07:58,870 --> 00:07:59,480
Run!

74
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,360
Young Master! Young Master!

75
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:02,750
Young Master!

76
00:08:04,350 --> 00:08:05,050
Young Master,

77
00:08:05,050 --> 00:08:07,020
it's me, Shiyi!

78
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,940
[Yue Shiyi, Moon Guard of Qingshan Manor]

79
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:07,830
Shiyi?

80
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:09,670
Young Master.

81
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:11,080
Shiyi.

82
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:13,980
Why are you guys here?

83
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:34,270
Chu.

84
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:42,870
Chu.

85
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:45,630
Come back with me.

86
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,900
Let's go back to Great Yan.

87
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:48,720
Yan Xun,

88
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:51,260
it's over between us.

89
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,630
Chu,

90
00:08:58,510 --> 00:09:00,200
we've faced death together,

91
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:02,390
sharing both joy and sorrow.

92
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,200
I don't believe there's anything

93
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:06,130
between us that can't be resolved.

94
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:08,530
Why are you being so resolute?

95
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:09,510
Yan Xun,

96
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:11,230
we used to walk side by side,

97
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:14,390
and we were each other's only comrades
and family.

98
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:15,240
The path we once walked

99
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,670
has already come to an end.

100
00:09:16,670 --> 00:09:17,630
Look behind.

101
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:20,750
We've long since gone our separate ways.

102
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:21,750
I was born a slave,

103
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:24,240
with only one goal in mind—
to abolish slavery and stop the wars,

104
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,960
so that even those with lives
as worthless as grass

105
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,560
could have the right to live.

106
00:09:27,810 --> 00:09:30,200
But all that remains in your eyes
is revenge.

107
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,720
You want to use fresh blood

108
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,150
to wash away the hatred of your family

109
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:34,320
and Great Yan.

110
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,150
Chu,

111
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:39,120
this world is inherently
a survival of the fittest.

112
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:41,360
There's never been such a thing
as justice or fairness.

113
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,490
There was no justice

114
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:44,360
when the Yan clan perished tragically

115
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,490
at Jiuyou Platform.

116
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,870
When we were imprisoned
in the Yingge Courtyard,

117
00:09:47,870 --> 00:09:48,720
with no one to depend on,

118
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,980
no one was there for us.

119
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:53,390
When I lost everything and was in despair,

120
00:09:54,010 --> 00:09:55,410
the only person by my side

121
00:09:56,130 --> 00:09:57,210
was you.

122
00:09:59,200 --> 00:09:59,870
Chu,

123
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:02,150
to me,

124
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,120
the world

125
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:06,150
and justice

126
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:10,200
are nothing compared
to the bond between us.

127
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:10,870
Yan Xun.

128
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:12,470
I was wrong.

129
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:15,150
I thought we shared the same ideals.

130
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,320
Because we depended on each other so much,

131
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:19,270
I saw you as my closest person.

132
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,210
But now we no longer walk the same path.

133
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,730
Please, let go of yourself,

134
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:26,600
and let go of me.

135
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,000
Chu.

136
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:51,120
I can guarantee that,

137
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:54,750
on your own,

138
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:58,360
you won't be able to fight your way out.

139
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:16,600
Zhuge Yue?

140
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,600
Yan Xun,

141
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:20,480
I didn't expect us to meet like this.

142
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,080
Xing.

143
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:23,810
You said yesterday

144
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,670
that you wanted me
to stay by your side forever.

145
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:26,590
I promise you.

146
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:29,590
I want you to stay by my side forever too.

147
00:11:29,630 --> 00:11:30,960
To the ends of the earth,

148
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,150
we live and die together.

149
00:11:34,430 --> 00:11:35,430
Zhuge Yue.

150
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,980
You shot an arrow at me
outside Zhenhuangcheng.

151
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,200
I paid you back at the frozen lake.

152
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,440
Now we are even.

153
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:46,320
If you leave now

154
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:49,100
and stop interfering between Chu and me,

155
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:51,840
I can pretend you were never here.

156
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:55,020
What happened between us
can be left in the past,

157
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:57,600
but if you persist in your ways,

158
00:11:58,510 --> 00:11:59,750
even your father...

159
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:00,630
Shut up!

160
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:04,080
You have no right to judge my father!

161
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,620
Attention, everyone!

162
00:12:05,870 --> 00:12:07,800
Whoever brings me Zhuge Yue's head

163
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:10,150
will be made
a Marquis of a Thousand Households!

164
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:10,960
Yes!

165
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:35,320
Let's go!

166
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,050
Retreat!

167
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,960
His Majesty is wise and brave.

168
00:12:57,300 --> 00:12:59,700
He is the one chosen by the gods
of Great Yan.

169
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:00,390
Yes.

170
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:01,630
I knew it.

171
00:13:01,870 --> 00:13:02,480
Under the guise

172
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,480
of a prisoner exchange, His Majesty

173
00:13:04,510 --> 00:13:05,790
captured Lincheng

174
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,360
and completely deceived
those from Great Yong.

175
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,510
Soon, we'll be able

176
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:11,720
to march all the way to Zhenhuangcheng

177
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:14,120
and avenge our fallen brothers.

178
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,720
Yes, avenge them!

179
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:18,320
Come on!

180
00:13:23,630 --> 00:13:24,960
Let's raise our glasses

181
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,550
to Great Yan

182
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,650
and our new King!

183
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,240
To His Majesty!

184
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,120
Your Majesty.

185
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:05,630
I heard you led the Black Eagle Army
and took Lincheng.

186
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:06,720
I'm here to congratulate you

187
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,750
and Great Yan.

188
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:14,240
We won a great victory at Lincheng.

189
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:17,150
Your Majesty, why aren't you celebrating
with the soldiers?

190
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:18,720
Did you see Chu?

191
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,110
What?

192
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,750
I saw her.

193
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:25,090
She also came to Lincheng.

194
00:14:25,370 --> 00:14:27,080
She rescued He Xiao.

195
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,540
Your Majesty, you saw her?

196
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,320
If you see her next time,

197
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:33,750
bring her back to me.

198
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,250
If she can't be brought back alive,

199
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,360
dead is fine.

200
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:41,640
Your Majesty.

201
00:14:43,790 --> 00:14:45,790
Haven't you always wanted her dead?

202
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:05,790
It should be fine, right?

203
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:07,510
It...

204
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:09,790
It should be fine.

205
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:11,790
Should?

206
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:13,550
You think I don't know?

207
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:15,510
An hour after taking the Huiyuan Pill,

208
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:16,550
one's vital energy is restored,

209
00:15:16,550 --> 00:15:17,720
but it shortens lifespan.

210
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:19,120
And you tell me it should be fine?

211
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:19,650
Don't...

212
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:21,390
Don't blame me.

213
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:22,240
It was Young Master Zhuge who insisted...

214
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:22,840
Xing.

215
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:24,320
I forced him.

216
00:15:24,780 --> 00:15:26,380
I had to save you at that time.

217
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,120
Xing!

218
00:15:40,910 --> 00:15:41,600
Xing.

219
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,000
It's me.

220
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,270
What do you want?

221
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,150
I came to tell you

222
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:51,270
everything that's happened
during all this time.

223
00:15:51,270 --> 00:15:52,870
I don't want to know anymore.

224
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:53,980
Leave.

225
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:18,970
Come on.

226
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:23,720
I never thought

227
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,360
I'd still be alive

228
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,720
to drink such fine wine.

229
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:28,390
After Young Master
fell into the frozen lake,

230
00:16:28,390 --> 00:16:31,120
Qingshan Manor sent us Moon Guards
to the front line.

231
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:33,050
Some of us died, some were injured,

232
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:35,850
and those captured suffered greatly.

233
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,460
Who would have thought

234
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:40,270
we'd see the Young Master again

235
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:42,990
and be here alive,
eating meat and drinking wine?

236
00:16:42,990 --> 00:16:43,870
To us being alive.

237
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:44,330
Cheers.

238
00:16:50,460 --> 00:16:51,460
How can you be here

239
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:53,480
drinking such fine wine without me?

240
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:55,270
How did you do it?

241
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:56,670
I didn't even notice,

242
00:16:56,670 --> 00:16:58,600
and the glass is already in your hand.

243
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:00,200
I just witnessed it.

244
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:02,670
Miss Fang's nickname is "Master Thief."

245
00:17:02,670 --> 00:17:05,069
Looks like there's nothing she can't take.

246
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:06,480
You...

247
00:17:11,109 --> 00:17:11,839
Tastes good.

248
00:17:15,349 --> 00:17:16,790
This is what happened

249
00:17:16,790 --> 00:17:18,310
after I fell into the frozen lake.

250
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:19,770
I was saved by King Ximeng,

251
00:17:20,030 --> 00:17:21,640
took the deadly poison Blood on Snow,

252
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:22,900
and became his shadow.

253
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:25,280
I promised to do 3 things for him

254
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,540
in exchange for the antidote.

255
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:34,920
Zhuge Yue,

256
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:38,680
why are you only telling me this now?

257
00:17:45,510 --> 00:17:46,510
Are you mute?

258
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:48,770
Why are you only saying it now?

259
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:52,030
Tell me! Why?

260
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:53,880
Why? Why?

261
00:18:10,450 --> 00:18:12,940
Zhuge Yue, promise me

262
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:16,270
that from now on, you won't hide
anything from me anymore,

263
00:18:16,270 --> 00:18:18,270
and you won't avoid me.

264
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,360
Did you hear me?

265
00:18:30,670 --> 00:18:31,470
Remember,

266
00:18:32,420 --> 00:18:34,750
you are not allowed
to hide anything from me anymore.

267
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:36,400
Considering your injuries,

268
00:18:37,710 --> 00:18:39,170
I will let you go this time.

269
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:54,540
Your Highness.

270
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:56,110
I...

271
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,570
Young Master Zhuge!

272
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:00,310
I went through a great deal of trouble

273
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:01,480
to save your life.

274
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:03,030
At the very least,
you should follow medical advice—

275
00:19:03,030 --> 00:19:06,090
no alcohol, no intimacy,
and avoid meat and heavy food.

276
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:07,830
This...

277
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:16,660
[Zhuge Yue] [Yan Xun] [Li Ce]

278
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,500
You don't understand.

279
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:23,480
Yan Xun and Her Highness
have known each other since childhood

280
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:25,030
and have gone through many hardships
together.

281
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:26,590
Even though they have now
turned against each other,

282
00:19:26,590 --> 00:19:28,750
the scar in Her Highness's heart
is still there.

283
00:19:28,750 --> 00:19:29,880
She can't forget him even if she wants to.

284
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:31,790
If Yan Xun keeps pushing like this,

285
00:19:31,790 --> 00:19:33,400
the embers could easily reignite.

286
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,240
If you ask me,

287
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:36,030
our princess will eventually
return to Great Yan

288
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:37,430
as its princess consort.

289
00:19:38,190 --> 00:19:39,460
She's not stupid.

290
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:41,480
Why would she go to a desolate place
like Great Yan

291
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,440
to be a princess consort?

292
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:45,160
It's better for her to stay in Biantang
and be the Crown Princess.

293
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:47,920
Our Crown Prince is wealthy
and quite romantic.

294
00:19:47,920 --> 00:19:49,210
She has suffered so much before.

295
00:19:49,210 --> 00:19:51,830
Only by staying with him
can she live a good life.

296
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:52,720
What do you think?

297
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,480
What do you think?

298
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:55,160
I... I choose Zhuge Yue.

299
00:19:55,270 --> 00:19:56,110
I think

300
00:19:56,110 --> 00:19:58,590
Miss Xing will definitely choose our boss.

301
00:19:58,590 --> 00:19:59,550
Why Zhuge Yue?

302
00:19:59,550 --> 00:20:02,350
Because our boss
is both talented and handsome.

303
00:20:02,350 --> 00:20:03,270
Yue Shiyi,

304
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,880
your boss is not even here.

305
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:06,740
Why are you still flattering him?

306
00:20:06,790 --> 00:20:07,590
Be honest,

307
00:20:07,680 --> 00:20:09,310
who are you really betting on?

308
00:20:09,310 --> 00:20:09,800
I...

309
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:12,150
You've left out an option in this bet.

310
00:20:13,270 --> 00:20:14,310
I saw everything.

311
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,400
I bet on the fourth one.

312
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,750
The fourth option?

313
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:24,960
Xing will not be anyone's
princess consort.

314
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,510
She will only be herself.

315
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,790
Why do I feel like

316
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:33,480
he's cursing our princess

317
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:35,700
to stay unmarried for her whole life?

318
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:03,200
Lady Chu,

319
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,960
it's so dusty outside.

320
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,840
We'd better close the window

321
00:21:06,870 --> 00:21:08,830
so the dust won't come in.

322
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:11,350
Stop!

323
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:19,030
General Chu.

324
00:21:19,870 --> 00:21:22,390
I'm getting a bit tired riding.

325
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:24,200
And the scenery here is not bad.

326
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:25,920
How about we switch?

327
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:28,790
Sure.

328
00:21:29,030 --> 00:21:30,200
I was just feeling a bit stuffy.

329
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:31,160
Let's switch.

330
00:21:35,070 --> 00:21:36,270
I get carsick easily.

331
00:21:36,510 --> 00:21:38,030
What do you mean, Yue Shiyi?

332
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:39,490
-Don't meddle.
-Alright.

333
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:41,680
Yue Shiyi, Fang Miaomiao,
get in the carriage.

334
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:42,880
I will ride the horse.

335
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:16,270
Don't you think

336
00:22:16,910 --> 00:22:19,110
Zhan Ziyu has been a bit strange lately?

337
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:20,780
Ever since the incident at the inn,

338
00:22:20,780 --> 00:22:22,440
he hasn't caused any trouble.

339
00:22:22,830 --> 00:22:25,090
He doesn't even come near our carriages.

340
00:22:25,550 --> 00:22:27,000
Isn't that a good thing, Your Highness?

341
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,990
Didn't he buy an eagle for a high price?

342
00:22:28,990 --> 00:22:30,720
He's been playing with it all the time.

343
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:31,440
I think

344
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:34,720
he was probably
scared out of his wits by you last time.

345
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:38,640
I don't think it's that simple.

346
00:22:39,070 --> 00:22:40,240
Rest assured, Your Highness.

347
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:42,270
We will arrive in Tangjing
in the blink of an eye.

348
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:43,680
As long as we enter the city safely,

349
00:22:43,680 --> 00:22:45,060
this hurdle will be behind us.

350
00:22:45,060 --> 00:22:47,510
No matter how he tries to cause trouble,
it won't work.

351
00:22:47,510 --> 00:22:49,130
[Tangjing]

352
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:54,550
Slow down.

353
00:23:02,270 --> 00:23:03,200
Your Highness.

354
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:06,860
Since you have returned safely
from this trip,

355
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:09,120
I will now return to the palace to report.

356
00:23:09,160 --> 00:23:10,820
I won't disturb Your Highness

357
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:13,550
and your distinguished guests any further.

358
00:23:13,550 --> 00:23:15,750
Thank you for your hard work, Lord Zhan.

359
00:23:25,050 --> 00:23:27,990
Give this to Lord Yu of the Ministry of Personnel's
Supervisory Department.

360
00:23:27,990 --> 00:23:29,850
Tell him it's Her Majesty's will.

361
00:23:30,180 --> 00:23:30,730
Yes.

362
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:37,480
I came especially to thank Her Majesty

363
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:39,700
for arranging the marriage
between the Prince of Luo and me.

364
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:41,480
[Linrui Palace]

365
00:23:39,790 --> 00:23:41,450
Please wait a moment, My Lady.

366
00:23:41,550 --> 00:23:42,680
Beauty Hu is inside

367
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:44,270
paying her respects to Her Majesty.

368
00:23:44,270 --> 00:23:46,270
I will go and announce your arrival.

369
00:23:55,060 --> 00:23:57,090
[Beauty Hu]

370
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:08,510
Let her in.

371
00:24:13,990 --> 00:24:16,990
You must be the girl
the Prince of Luo is about to marry.

372
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:18,900
Your Highness, you are...

373
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,680
It doesn't matter if you don't know me.

374
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,030
I know you.

375
00:24:23,440 --> 00:24:26,240
You are the famous Princess Chun'er
of Great Yong,

376
00:24:26,250 --> 00:24:29,180
who almost married the new King
of Great Yan, Yan Xun.

377
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,000
Pardon me.

378
00:24:32,120 --> 00:24:34,180
I shouldn't have touched a sore spot.

379
00:24:34,510 --> 00:24:35,750
But it's all good now.

380
00:24:36,320 --> 00:24:39,440
You will soon be the Princess Consort of Luo
in our Biantang.

381
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:42,040
However, there is one thing
that surprises me.

382
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:43,790
You don't look...

383
00:24:44,190 --> 00:24:46,700
like Princess Fu at all.

384
00:24:46,890 --> 00:24:50,240
The Prince of Luo has been deeply in love
with Princess Fu for years.

385
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:52,120
Why did he suddenly
have a change of heart?

386
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:53,050
What did you say?

387
00:24:54,540 --> 00:24:56,140
Don't tell me you don't know.

388
00:24:56,240 --> 00:24:59,100
The Prince of Luo and Princess Fu
were once engaged.

389
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:02,490
The Prince of Luo has remained unmarried
for years because of Princess Fu.

390
00:25:02,490 --> 00:25:05,170
Now that Princess Fu
has been brought back,

391
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:07,030
we all thought

392
00:25:07,030 --> 00:25:10,560
the Prince of Luo would resume
his engagement with Princess Fu.

393
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:12,440
Is the Princess Fu you're talking about

394
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:14,570
the one in the Crown Prince's Mansion?

395
00:25:14,750 --> 00:25:17,010
The Prince of Luo was once engaged to her?

396
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:18,480
Beauty Hu.

397
00:25:19,350 --> 00:25:20,080
Her Majesty?

398
00:25:25,310 --> 00:25:26,350
Your Majesty.

399
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,110
Come here.

400
00:25:33,720 --> 00:25:34,960
What did you just say?

401
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,200
Your Majesty,

402
00:25:36,350 --> 00:25:36,880
I...

403
00:25:41,030 --> 00:25:42,000
Your Majesty,

404
00:25:42,190 --> 00:25:43,560
I was wrong.

405
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:44,310
Servants.

406
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:46,830
Beauty Hu has behaved improperly
in words and actions

407
00:25:46,830 --> 00:25:48,110
and slandered a prince.

408
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:49,640
According to palace rules,

409
00:25:49,850 --> 00:25:51,280
slap her 20 times.

410
00:25:51,680 --> 00:25:52,680
Your Majesty,

411
00:25:53,110 --> 00:25:54,350
I was wrong!

412
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:55,790
Your Majesty,

413
00:25:56,110 --> 00:25:57,400
I was wrong!

414
00:25:57,750 --> 00:25:59,350
Please forgive me!

415
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:00,750
Your Majesty!

416
00:26:01,110 --> 00:26:02,830
Your Majesty!

417
00:26:40,190 --> 00:26:41,190
How could this be?

418
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:42,830
Chun'er!

419
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:46,590
Chun'er.

420
00:26:47,430 --> 00:26:48,400
You misunderstood.

421
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,070
This portrait is...

422
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:50,590
It's Princess Fu in this portrait.

423
00:26:50,590 --> 00:26:52,650
You were engaged to her, weren't you?

424
00:26:54,720 --> 00:26:55,850
Then do you know that

425
00:26:56,220 --> 00:26:58,490
the Princess Fu in the Crown Prince's Mansion
is an impostor,

426
00:26:58,490 --> 00:27:01,350
and that she is Chu Qiao,
a convicted slave from Great Yong?

427
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,160
I know.

428
00:27:02,830 --> 00:27:04,520
Her Majesty had suspected it long ago

429
00:27:04,520 --> 00:27:06,180
and called me to identify her.

430
00:27:06,350 --> 00:27:09,790
She and the Crown Prince
privately asked me to help cover it up.

431
00:27:09,790 --> 00:27:12,390
You actually testified
for a convicted slave?

432
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,030
Yes.

433
00:27:15,830 --> 00:27:19,030
So you like Princess Fu.

434
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:21,440
And because she looks like Princess Fu,

435
00:27:21,440 --> 00:27:22,790
you like her too,

436
00:27:24,030 --> 00:27:24,960
don't you?

437
00:27:25,350 --> 00:27:26,160
No, Chun'er.

438
00:27:26,240 --> 00:27:27,030
I don't.

439
00:27:27,890 --> 00:27:29,130
I did like Fu before,

440
00:27:29,550 --> 00:27:30,750
but I know very well that she is not...

441
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:31,790
Then burn it!

442
00:27:42,330 --> 00:27:44,160
You claim that you like me!

443
00:27:44,190 --> 00:27:45,470
You liar!

444
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:46,850
Li Yan,

445
00:27:47,350 --> 00:27:48,680
you don't have to love me.

446
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:50,880
You can have someone else in your heart,

447
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,480
but it can't be her.

448
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:53,880
It can't be Chu Qiao!

449
00:28:07,010 --> 00:28:08,640
My Lady, your wedding is coming up soon.

450
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:09,790
The crowd here is quite mixed.

451
00:28:09,790 --> 00:28:11,070
We should head back early,

452
00:28:11,070 --> 00:28:12,680
or His Highness will be worried.

453
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:13,590
Why go back?

454
00:28:13,670 --> 00:28:15,000
He won't worry about me.

455
00:28:15,830 --> 00:28:17,270
I'm just a substitute.

456
00:28:17,410 --> 00:28:19,540
The person in his heart is Princess Fu.

457
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:21,240
Your Highness,
you shouldn't think like that.

458
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:22,680
Since His Highness met you,

459
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:24,610
he has changed a lot.

460
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:27,880
Miss, have you seen this person?

461
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:28,680
No.

462
00:28:29,270 --> 00:28:30,130
I'll take this.

463
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:32,400
Miss,

464
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:33,800
have you seen this woman?

465
00:28:39,450 --> 00:28:42,740
[Prince of Luo's Mansion]

466
00:29:05,170 --> 00:29:06,900
Your Highness! Your Highness!

467
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:08,500
Your Highness,

468
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:10,070
this is the nuptial wine
for you and His Highness.

469
00:29:10,070 --> 00:29:12,000
You can't drink it all by yourself.

470
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,200
I want more!

471
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:14,750
Bring more wine!

472
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:17,270
Your Highness, you are really drunk.

473
00:29:17,270 --> 00:29:18,670
You can't drink anymore.

474
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:23,780
Your Highness,

475
00:29:23,880 --> 00:29:26,030
this wedding fan can only be removed
when His Highness comes.

476
00:29:26,030 --> 00:29:27,960
Otherwise it would bring bad luck.

477
00:29:30,590 --> 00:29:31,400
Chunxing.

478
00:29:33,570 --> 00:29:37,090
Do you know how many times
I've been married?

479
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:40,000
Three times.

480
00:29:41,070 --> 00:29:42,740
This is the 3rd time.

481
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:48,950
The first time, on my wedding day,

482
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:50,920
snow was falling heavily.

483
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:56,720
My groom rebelled
and led troops against my father.

484
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,270
I begged him,

485
00:29:59,550 --> 00:30:01,000
but he wouldn't listen.

486
00:30:02,860 --> 00:30:06,050
Instead, he threw the wedding robe
I made for him

487
00:30:06,080 --> 00:30:07,320
onto the ground,

488
00:30:09,120 --> 00:30:11,990
letting horses trample over it.

489
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,060
Your Highness!

490
00:30:17,180 --> 00:30:19,180
He walked past me so coldly,

491
00:30:19,210 --> 00:30:21,450
so decisively.

492
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:23,850
He walked past my body

493
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:26,290
and shattered my heart.

494
00:30:27,750 --> 00:30:28,750
The second time,

495
00:30:30,680 --> 00:30:31,830
I carefully arranged

496
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:35,070
a fake wedding for myself.

497
00:30:38,810 --> 00:30:40,870
Your Highness, you are really drunk.

498
00:30:41,030 --> 00:30:41,590
Here.

499
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:43,030
Here.

500
00:30:49,310 --> 00:30:50,000
Chunxing.

501
00:30:51,350 --> 00:30:52,310
You know what?

502
00:30:53,750 --> 00:30:55,480
I finally got married.

503
00:31:32,570 --> 00:31:34,970
What else is there for me
to look forward to?

504
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:43,490
Your Highness, be careful!

505
00:31:46,550 --> 00:31:48,150
Your Highness, your foot...

506
00:31:49,160 --> 00:31:49,750
Chun'er!

507
00:31:51,700 --> 00:31:53,270
Chun'er, are you alright?

508
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:25,960
Chun'er.

509
00:32:27,120 --> 00:32:29,070
If you don't want to get married yet,

510
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:31,550
we can pretend
today's wedding never happened.

511
00:32:31,550 --> 00:32:33,010
I can keep waiting for you,

512
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:35,200
until you fall in love with me,

513
00:32:36,310 --> 00:32:38,570
until the day
you truly want to be my wife.

514
00:33:03,830 --> 00:33:05,590
I heard Her Majesty likes jade,

515
00:33:05,830 --> 00:33:07,400
so I specially found a fine piece.

516
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:09,080
Her Majesty is not in the palace.

517
00:33:09,080 --> 00:33:13,210
Princess Consort of Luo, please follow me
to the hall and wait for a moment.

518
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:23,220
Your Highness, please have some tea.

519
00:33:26,460 --> 00:33:28,250
[Qifeng Palace]

520
00:33:35,620 --> 00:33:37,850
I have already handed the evidence
obtained from the trip to Qiongzhou

521
00:33:37,850 --> 00:33:39,550
to Lord Yu of the Ministry of Personnel.

522
00:33:39,550 --> 00:33:41,270
That King Ximeng is a fake.

523
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:43,000
He was sent by Ximeng to Biantang

524
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:45,290
to obtain Director Zhang's
manufacturing compendium.

525
00:33:45,290 --> 00:33:47,010
I just don't know how he

526
00:33:47,040 --> 00:33:49,040
got involved with the Crown Prince.

527
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:53,880
This son of mine is quite something.

528
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:56,790
I really underestimated him.

529
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:58,260
There is another thing

530
00:33:58,510 --> 00:34:00,200
that I also find very strange.

531
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:02,000
What is it?

532
00:34:02,020 --> 00:34:04,640
In the team
of the Crown Prince and Ximeng this time,

533
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,240
I didn't see Princess Fu,

534
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:07,610
that Chu Qiao.

535
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:09,440
And as far as I know,

536
00:34:09,850 --> 00:34:11,469
she is not
in the Crown Prince's Mansion either.

537
00:34:11,469 --> 00:34:14,030
Are you saying Chu Qiao is missing?

538
00:34:15,030 --> 00:34:15,670
Yes.

539
00:34:17,020 --> 00:34:19,310
I worry she will affect our grand plan.

540
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:27,889
Then let's strike first

541
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:29,440
and do it quickly

542
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:32,070
to avoid any complications.

543
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:33,590
As long as we solidify

544
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:37,170
the Crown Prince's charges of treason
and collusion with the enemy,

545
00:34:37,170 --> 00:34:38,730
even 10 Chu Qiaos

546
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:40,760
won't be able to save him.

547
00:34:46,429 --> 00:34:48,949
Today is the 6th, right?

548
00:34:56,030 --> 00:34:57,110
Today is the 6th.

549
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:58,920
Are the carriages ready?

550
00:34:59,470 --> 00:35:00,320
Your Majesty,

551
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:02,400
the carriages are ready outside.

552
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:04,360
But today is the Greater Heat.

553
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:06,150
For years, you've gone to chant sutras

554
00:35:06,150 --> 00:35:08,880
for Crown Prince Maocheng
on the sixth of every month.

555
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:11,010
But it's exceptionally hot this year.

556
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,630
I'm afraid your body

557
00:35:12,630 --> 00:35:13,960
can't handle the journey.

558
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:14,630
It's fine.

559
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,550
Let's go to Tianlong Temple.

560
00:35:16,670 --> 00:35:17,630
Your Majesty!

561
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:21,670
Your Majesty!

562
00:35:21,670 --> 00:35:23,800
I have something important to report!

563
00:35:24,070 --> 00:35:26,000
Don't you know what day it is today?

564
00:35:26,670 --> 00:35:29,150
Rushing into the palace so recklessly.

565
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:33,190
Beauty,

566
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:35,010
what happened to your face?

567
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:37,760
Your Majesty,

568
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,480
I know very well

569
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:41,880
that today is the day
you go to Tianlong Temple

570
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:44,280
to chant sutras for Crown Prince Maocheng.

571
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:46,550
Your devotion
is known to the heavens and the earth.

572
00:35:46,550 --> 00:35:47,960
But do you know

573
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:49,480
what Her Majesty has been doing

574
00:35:49,480 --> 00:35:51,070
every time you're away?

575
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:54,800
What do you mean?

576
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:06,910
Greetings, Your Majesty!

577
00:36:06,910 --> 00:36:08,180
Greetings, Beauty Hu!

578
00:36:16,010 --> 00:36:18,270
Where is the Empress? Why isn't she here?

579
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,260
Her Majesty...

580
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,810
Her Majesty is resting.

581
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:25,130
You lowly servant!

582
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:56,760
Empress.

583
00:36:57,620 --> 00:36:59,870
What are you two women doing?

584
00:37:00,070 --> 00:37:00,630
I...

585
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:04,340
I'm keeping Her Majesty company
in the bath.

586
00:37:41,690 --> 00:37:43,160
Today isn't a festival.

587
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:45,060
Why did you release so many sky lanterns?

588
00:37:45,060 --> 00:37:45,910
Zhuge Yue,

589
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:47,800
what's your plan?

590
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,400
I will never willingly

591
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:52,960
an incompetent coward!

592
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:53,840
I am not!

593
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:57,540
Her Majesty orders

594
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:59,760
that the Queen of Lingyue
and the false King Ximeng

595
00:37:59,760 --> 00:38:01,000
be arrested immediately!

596
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:02,360
Since you have moved on,

597
00:38:02,860 --> 00:38:04,420
how could I be dwelling on it?

